6. QUIZ ANSWER KEY
==================================================
 
The correct answer for each week's quiz (Day 5) follows this pattern:
BBAABABA
 
Week:    1  2  3  4  5  6  7  8
Answer:  B  B  A  A  B  A  B  A
Prompt#: 5  12 19 26 33 40 47 54
 
This pattern is IDENTICAL across all 4 purposes within C1.
The pattern may differ in C2, C3, etc.
 
Purpose for the pattern: prevents students from guessing without
reading by removing any predictable sequence.
 
Stored in: correct_answer column in the prompts table.
Used by: teacher portal when reviewing student quiz responses.
NOT used for: automated answer checking (no automation on quiz).
 
 
